{"slideshow_credits": null, "snippet": "Under threat of an honor killing, a young couple cannot get a visa to leave Afghanistan.", "abstract": "News Analysis; plight of newlywed Afghan couple Zakia and Mohammad Ali is common among many would-be migrants who wish to flee to Europe, yet cannot apply for asylum unless they leave their home countries; Alis do not wish to risk dangers involved in fleeing country without visa; situation is due to clause in Geneva conventions requiring that persecuted parties must be outside country of nationality. ", "section_name": "Sunday Review", "print_page": "3", "document_type": "article", "byline": {"person": [{"firstname": "Rod", "role": "reported", "lastname": "NORDLAND", "rank": 1, "organization": ""}], "original": "By ROD NORDLAND"}, "web_url": "http://www.nytimes.com/2015/12/06/sunday-review/in-danger-in-afghanistan-unable-to-flee.html", "lead_paragraph": "Under threat of an honor killing, a young couple cannot get a visa to leave Afghanistan.", "headline": {"print_headline": "In Danger in Afghanistan, Unable to Flee", "main": "In Danger in Afghanistan, Unable to Flee", "content_kicker": "News Analysis", "kicker": "News Analysis"}, "_id": "56634f1938f0d8161e789440", "word_count": "1198", "multimedia": [{"height": 126, "url": "images/2015/12/06/opinion/sunday/06nordland/06nordland-thumbWide.jpg", "legacy": {"wideheight": "126", "wide": "images/2015/12/06/opinion/sunday/06nordland/06nordland-thumbWide.jpg", "widewidth": "190"}, "subtype": "wide", "width": 190, "type": "image"}, {"height": 400, "url": "images/2015/12/06/opinion/sunday/06nordland/06nordland-articleLarge.jpg", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2015/12/06/opinion/sunday/06nordland/06nordland-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": "600", "xlargeheight": "400"}, "subtype": "xlarge", "width": 600, "type": "image"}, {"height": 75, "url": "images/2015/12/06/opinion/sunday/06nordland/06nordland-thumbStandard.jpg", "legacy": {"thumbnail": "images/2015/12/06/opinion/sunday/06nordland